```

**Time Complexity**: O(n²) in worst case, O(n) in best case (if array is already sorted).

---

### **Optimized Code (Bubble Sort with Early Termination)**
```ts
function bubbleSortOptimized(arr: number[]): number[] {
  let n = arr.length;
  let swapped = true;
  let i = 0;
  while (swapped) {
    swapped = false;
    for (let j = 0; j < n - i - 1; j++) {
      if (arr[j] > arr[j + 1]) {
        [arr[j], arr[j + 1]] = [arr[j + 1], arr[j]];
        swapped = true;
      }
    }
    i++;
  }
  return arr;
}
```

**Time Complexity**: O(n²) in worst case, O(n) in best case (if array is already sorted).

